A man was arrested in the Eastern Cape for allegedly killing his father in a knife fight! Willowvale Police arrested the 37-year-old man after a fight between him and his father (67) broke out in Xonyeni Village in Willowvale, Eastern Cape on Friday (28 September). According to police, both drew their knives and began to stab each other The father was fatally wounded and reportedly died on the scene. Police are investigating a murder charge. The suspect is expected to appear before the Willowvale Magistrate Court on Monday (1 October). 